            <!-- DESCRIPTION START -->
            <description>
                
                    <ul>
                        <li>Added support for Nobara 41.</li>
                        <li>Fixed uppercase file extension not correctly detected.</li>
                        <li>Fixed the conversion of files with spaces in their names.</li>
                        <li>Added support for Intel iGPUs.</li>
                        <li>Fixed support for Nvidia mobile GPUs.</li>
                        <li>Added support for more AMD iGPUs.</li>
                        <li>Added for using .run installer wizard file.</li>
